## 3. Step-by-Step Ulnar Build Instructions

### Phase 0: Foundation (1–2 days)
1. Fork Mission Control repo as base (32 panels, real-time, SQLite, RBAC, Docker).
2. Create Sovereign Monad repo: `/smcc` (Next.js 15 + TypeScript + Tailwind + shadcn/ui + Recharts + Zustand + KafkaJS).
3. Import Sci-Fi Dashboard Kit CSS variables + custom panel components.
4. Docker Compose v3 with frontend, backend, SQLite/PostgreSQL, Kafka (Redpanda dev), Redis (optional).

### Phase 1: Core Ulnar Backbone (3–5 days)
5. Implement LangGraph orchestration engine with Sovereign Monad nodes.
6. Build live Kafka Wiring Diagram (React Flow / Cytoscape.js).
7. Deploy Gnosis Integrity Layer service + axiom drift detector.
8. Create Skills Matrix with shared capability highlighter.

### Phase 2: Builder & Governance (4–6 days)
9. Integrate unified no/low-code builder (Dust visual canvas + Relevance AI team builder + Copilot NL prompts).
10. Add Quality Gates, RBAC, enterprise compliance checks.
11. Implement Build Pipeline Tracker (BLOCKED/PARTIAL/DONE synced to roadmap JSON).

### Phase 3: Monitoring, Analytics & On-Chain (5–7 days)
12. Add Dune-style SQL editor + Blockworks metrics against Kafka/agent logs.
13. Chainalysis-inspired integrity risk/alert engine.
14. Build full cost estimator (infra + RPC + gas + token modeling).
15. Add on-chain attestation dashboard.

### Phase 4: Polish & Deployment (3–4 days)
16. Apply refined cyberpunk UI (neon glows, pulse animations, toggleable scanlines).
17. Add headless API + multi-channel deployment.
18. End-to-end testing (agent workflows, drift simulation, cost accuracy).
19. Package as single `docker-compose up` with guided onboarding wizard.
20. Self-hosted first; optional enterprise cloud variant with SSO.

### Minimal Sovereign Tech Stack
Next.js 15, LangGraph, KafkaJS, React Flow, Tailwind, Recharts, better-sqlite3, Docker. All open-source, no cloud lock-in.

